{"tid":1939180,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"3月21日晩襲警案被告可以保釋 手足被捕時手、手肘、上身、胸骨、下身均受傷","createTime":"2020-03-23T04:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T19:40:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8d372b17b3774efd144a2c874675b8ca5ffa26","tid":1939180,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"#屯門裁判法院第一庭 #張潔宜署理主任裁判官<br />\n#20200321元朗 #新案件<br />\n曾(42)<br />\n襲警<br />\n第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》第36(b)條<br />\n<br />\n控罪：被控於2020年3月21日，在香港新界元朗鳳琴街18號玉龍樓地下7-11便利店外襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即督察18917李顯揚</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n投訴：被捕時手、手肘、上身、胸骨、下身均受傷，需入院5個半小時接受治療<br />\n<br />\n⭕️保釋批准⭕️<br />\n保釋條件如下：<br />\n擔保金$20,000<br />\n2位人事擔保各$20,000<br />\n（共$60,000）<br />\n不離港<br />\n交出所有旅遊證件<br />\n在報稱地址居住<br />\n任何地址更改須在24小時前通知<br />\n每週報到1次<br />\n宵禁令0000-0600<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至5月4日屯門裁判法院第一庭再訊"},{"pid":"a54e7e93ff49c8108f2c23f4b97af3e228d8dd2e","tid":1939180,"uid":321059,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"被捕時手、手肘、上身、胸骨、下身均受傷，需入院5個半小時接受治療<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">究竟係邊個襲擊邊個？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d612f14196a6eed6b63acdf268ca6c0ae040e438","tid":1939180,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a54e7e93ff49c8108f2c23f4b97af3e228d8dd2e","tid":1939180,"uid":321059,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"被捕時手、手肘、上身、胸骨、下身均受傷，需入院5個半小時接受治療<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">究竟係邊個襲擊邊個？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji